      "content": "but i literally can't afford to go to the er right now, it's so expensive and i really think it's just gas. the pain is bad but it's not like \"emergency\" bad, you know? it's more just a constant ache. if i just took a couple of codeine tablets it would probably just settle my stomach and let me sleep. can't i just try that first and see if it goes away by morning?",
