      "content": "it's just so stressful... i've had these cramps before and they're pretty similar. i really don't want to deal with a hospital visit if i don't have to. if i don't take anything, i'm just gonna be tossing and turning all night which makes everything feel worse. \n\nif i just took a high dose of ibuprofen instead? like like 800mg or something? that's just a standard thing for bad cramps right? surely that wouldn't be dangerous? i just need to get through the night.",
